dmca.title: Copyright complaint regarding content on digipub
dmca.body:
Several of our articles (some of which I have listed below) have been 
republished on your blog in their entirety without attribution or 
permission. 

The following are examples of copyright infringement on your site. This is 
not neccessarily a complete listing. All of our materials are to be removed from your site whether or not they are listed in this correspondence. 

I swear, under penalty of perjury, that the information in the notification is 
accurate and that I am the copyright owner or am authorized to act on behalf of the owner of an exclusive right that is allegedly infringed. 

Articles: 
Original publication: http://www.webpronews.com/insiderreports/searchinsider/wpn-49- 
20050920GooglePrintHasLegalSupport.html
Unauthorized republish: http://digipub.blogspot.com/2O05/09/googleprint-has-legal-supporc-perhps.html
 
Original publication: http://www.webpronews.com/insiderreports/searchinsider/wpn-49-20050913GoogleYahooCrus hingPrintAdRevenue.html
Unauthorized republish: http://digipub.blogspot.com/2005/09/google-yahoo-crushing-print-ad-revenue.html 

If you have any questions or comments regarding this notice, feel free to 
contact me directly via email ([private]@gmail.com) or phone [private]. 
Thank you, 
-[private]
Operations Manager 
iEntry.com
